metadata.name: Serenity
metadata.description:
Serenity is a calm and peaceful breeze,  
A moment of stillness that puts our hearts at ease,  
It's the gentle whisper of leaves on a tree,  
And the quiet lull of a tranquil sea.

Serenity by Vaarin Thakral

Made with: Photoshop & Ai  
File Details : 1:1 png, 2048x2048px
